3. cs.COM (Computational Complexity) - The paper involves analyzing the performance of different relaying protocols, which may involve computational complexity.
4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper deals with the performance analysis of communication systems, which is a topic of interest in systems and control.
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper may involve analyzing the performance of communication protocols for multimedia applications.
